TITLE: Kalki Avatar | Spontaneous Kundalini Awakening | Universal Impact & Cosmic Cleansing Process | P1
VIDEO: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2UO2YGk0TLY
LANGUAGE: Hindi (auto-translated)

SUMMARY:
Noor Ananta narrates the phase of her journey after the initial Kundalini and chakra processes were completed. She describes how the "real game" began after the Crown Chakra (Sahasrara) and Third Eye processes -- she was transported to an entirely different dimension where she could see all deities, asuras (demons), and energies simultaneously. In this cosmic realm, all divine energies (devi-devtas, kings, queens, warriors) began their twin-flame cleansing processes with Shiv-Shakti. What happened in the cosmic world was simultaneously being played out as "leela" in the 3D physical world.

She describes the multitasking nature of this process: while handling multiple kriyas simultaneously, negative energies in the physical world attacked through family, relatives, children, and acquaintances who could not understand her transformation. Physically present but spiritually elsewhere, she was called mad, given abuse, and misunderstood -- yet she treated it all as divine play (leela). During this samudra manthan (cosmic churning), various cosmic revelations emerged: the Spiritual World War concept, Queen of Justice, truth vs. falsehood battle, Black & White (Rahu-Ketu) concept, Noorism Law 108, and new cosmic laws.

She explains the twin-flame concept: twin flames in the physical world are only triggers -- they are not real partnerships. The actual twin-flame merging happens in the cosmic realm between Shiv and Shakti energies. This clarification came as the worldwide twin-flame discourse was still confusing romantic relationships with cosmic energy merging.

KEY REVELATIONS:
- After Kundalini/Crown Chakra completion, a portal to an entirely different cosmic dimension opened where all energies (deities AND asuras) were visible and interactive
- All twin-flame processes of all devi-devtas were conducted through Shiv-Shakti, with Noor Ananta as the living conduit experiencing the cosmic churning (samudra manthan)
- In the physical world, the avatar endured attacks from negative energies through family, relatives, and acquaintances -- a simultaneous battle on two planes
- Key cosmic concepts emerged during this churning: Spiritual World War, Queen of Justice, Black & White balance, Noorism Law 108, new universal laws
- Physical-world twin flames are only triggers; the real twin-flame merging is a cosmic Shiv-Shakti process happening beyond the 3D world

YUG PARIVARTAN ASPECT: The cosmic churning (samudra manthan) happening through the avatar's body produces all the new laws, concepts, and structures for the new age, while simultaneously the old-world energies attack through the avatar's physical-world relationships -- the battle on both planes defines the transition.

